description: Registers the specified directory. This operation is asynchronous and returns before the WorkSpace directory is registered. If this is the first time you are registering a directory, you will need to create the workspaces_DefaultRole role before you can register a directory. For more information, see Creating the workspaces_DefaultRole Role.

parameters.name: SubnetIds
parameters.description: The identifiers of the subnets for your virtual private cloud (VPC). Make sure that the subnets are in supported Availability Zones. The subnets must also be in separate Availability Zones. If these conditions are not met, you will receive an OperationNotSupportedException error. (string) ---

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: The tags associated with the directory. (dict) --- Describes a tag. The key of the tag. Value (string) --- The value of the tag.

parameters.name: MicrosoftEntraConfig
parameters.description: The details about Microsoft Entra config. TenantId (string) --- The identifier of the tenant. ApplicationConfigSecretArn (string) --- The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the application config.

nested_params.name: ApplicationConfigSecretArn
nested_params.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the application config.

parameters.name: ActiveDirectoryConfig
parameters.description: The active directory config of the directory. The name of the domain. Indicates the secret ARN on the service account.

nested_params.name: ServiceAccountSecretArn
nested_params.description: Indicates the secret ARN on the service account.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: The registration status of the WorkSpace directory.
